16:39.620 --> 16:41.200
the guy in the heavy space armor is going down.

16:41.280 --> 16:43.020
All friends come to rescue him, you know?

16:44.320 --> 16:47.560
And in Bill, the guy goes in a swamp and the soldier in the marching by says,

16:47.620 --> 16:48.380
help me, help me.

16:48.420 --> 16:51.700
And they walk on by, says, Bob your buddy week.

16:51.700 --> 16:54.720
And they say it's always Bob your buddy week.

16:54.840 --> 16:56.200
And that's just, we should say in the army, you know?

16:56.720 --> 16:59.820
I mean, it always is.

17:00.080 --> 17:00.960
It's every man for himself.

