19:34.740 --> 19:38.000
And so I said it in the year 1999 in New York.

19:38.620 --> 19:42.640
I made some millennial novel, bring a lot of overtones, you know, the millennium,

19:42.880 --> 19:44.160
coming of Christ and the sort of thing.

19:45.000 --> 19:46.700
