20:06.900 --> 20:08.780
Harry, they're trapped up to take four pages of the lecture.

20:09.300 --> 20:13.560
So I just put in four pages, a copy of about a thousand words, two pages in the book,

20:14.060 --> 20:16.020
telling you how it worked out that way.

20:16.080 --> 20:19.960
And I said, my one little lecture right there, having done that little lecture,

20:20.680 --> 20:23.400
it was, in a sense, a work of propaganda and art.

20:23.760 --> 20:25.060
If you have better the art, you have better the propaganda.

20:25.800 --> 20:26.820
1984 is propaganda.

20:27.940 --> 20:28.920
On the beach is propaganda.

20:28.920 --> 20:30.780
Both art, you get the message.

20:31.320 --> 20:31.820
And that was it.

20:32.000 --> 20:34.000
